suno aaj tumse ek dil ki baat kehni hai 
jab se tum meri zindagi mein aaye ho, kaafi kuch badal hai ,
main humesha se stable nahi tha, bahut ji unstable aur unpractical insaan hua karta tha,
jisey nahi pata tha ki usey kaise deal karna hai apni problems se,
kaise mushkil ghadi mein apne dimaag ko shaant kar khud ko sambhalna hai.
kitni buri adatein thi jo chhuti hain, kitna bhatka hua karta tha, aaj mere raaste saaf hote 
dikhayi de rahe hain, aur waja tum ho....
mujhe nahi pata manzil kitni door hai lekin main chahta hun ki manzil tak ka jo safar ho wo tumhare saath ho,
kyunki saath tumhara lajawaab hai.
tumhare sath cjalne mein ek sukoon mehsus hota hai mujhe, bhale hi haathon mein haanth na ho par tumhara aas paas hona bahut mayine rakhta hai 
mujhe jo aaj tumhare leye mehsus ho raha hai, usey lekar main bahut khus hun najaane kyun mujhe koi umeed mahi kisi bhi tarha ki main bas chahta hun to itna ki  tum khus raho !
tumhara chehra hansta khilkhilata rahe, jhoomta muskurata rahe mujhe aur koi guzaarish nahi hai khuda se.
mere in jazbaaton ko kabhi koi nahi badal sakta hai wo tumhare liye hain aur humesha rahenge.
tum chaho to ek bar mujhe pe bharosa kar ke dekho, shayad is duniya mein har koi tumhara dil todne ke liye haath aagey nahi 
badata, ye baat main sabit karna chahta hoon bas ek mauke ki talaash hai. 
aagar tum chaho to mat do main dur se dekh muskurata rahunga, na jaane kitne waqt tak par main usme bhi khus hun. 
bas ye baatein tumhe batani thi ye jazbaat tumhe bayaan karne the kyunki pyaar ko apne dil mein qaid karne ki kala mujhe mein nahi .
or han I LOVE YOU FAUZIYA MERI JAAN.....